<p>
Then Vaillant declared that sobriety isn't even really the goal:
<p>
<blockquote>
<font color="black" face="Lucida,Utopia bold,Utopia,Helvetica,Charter,Arial,sans-serif,Sans Serif,New Century Schoolbook">
Finally, and most important, it must be remembered that abstinence
is a means, not an end. It is a puritanical goal that removes but
