the first step, then the second, and so on until you reach the 12th, then you're on
the different floor where you wanted to go and you're done with the steps. Instead,
with &quot;The 12 Steps&quot;, when you finish the 12th step you
just arrive back at step 1 again, and start all over. And then you just keep doing
this forever.

